feed.title: Urban Fertilizer: Pigeon Guano
feed.description:
I am monitoring pigeon guano depositories in the city for collection purposes. Pigeon guano is an excellent fertilizer that is available locally and at zero cost. It is also considered a public health concern and is undesirable to many humans. 

Please inform me if you have noticed a depository of pigeon guano.
